Responsive Design:

-Set your margin to auto
-Set your width to max width
-CHanging properties from set values to
autocorrecting allows you to implement responsive design

Media Query-allows you to set CSS styles
that activate when the browser is a certain
width
   example:
   @media (max-width: 500px) {
    body {
      background:red
    }
   }



